lead_paragraph: JANER--Raphael "Ray" Joseph, passed away peacefully on March 2, 2016. All services will be private and are being handled by Parsell Funeral Homes and Crematorium, Atkins-Lodge Chapel, Lewes, DE. Please visit Ray's Life Memorial Webpage to read his full obituary and to sign his online guestbook at: parsellfuneralhomes.com. 1/3
